elements.text: I'm looking for project ideas with Julia for parallel computing

text: Welcome! What sorts of projects interest you?  Hacking on the language and packages themselves is certainly one way you could go — but you could also just try some parallel computation tasks.  And there the sky is the limit — just depends on what interests you
